{"id": 914, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都试过哪些“亲测有效”？", "description": "涤荡心灵有比去西藏更快更省钱的办法，做几组硬拉；求得内心平静也有比找仁波切更有效的办法，擦几双皮鞋；治疗失眠不用吃安眠药，看几分钟天线宝宝国语版。——@二逼瓦西里（题图来自：jeannie phan）", "record_count": 5621, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703152329q7hyWa9t5ZJcp1PN.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-04-15T11:04:48Z", "options": [{"id": 67840, "content": "无印良品的香薰机真的能提升幸福感િિ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569844}, {"id": 68096, "content": "穿着高更鞋跑步?脚更累。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 393720}, {"id": 68352, "content": "早睡早起，肾功能会变强。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 558464}, {"id": 67841, "content": "帮助困难的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562930}, {"id": 68865, "content": "吃到好吃的东西，身上所有的毛孔都张开了的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 574063}, {"id": 67842, "content": "困的时候吃鸭脖比咖啡还有效", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454701}, {"id": 68098, "content": "睡觉能缓解心情 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410155}, {"id": 69890, "content": "打吹欠时被打断就再也打不出来了，憋到流眼泪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 580124}, {"id": 68099, "content": "网易云音乐比其他同类产品更值得拥有", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410155}, {"id": 68100, "content": "下载软件破解版", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565348}, {"id": 67845, "content": "晒晒被子真的更容易睡着", "image": null, "praise_count": 162, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 564069}, {"id": 67846, "content": "星巴克的咖啡真的比较好喝", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 552544}, {"id": 68870, "content": "给吃水果的女友BJ味道更好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573477}, {"id": 68103, "content": "吃吃吃解百忧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75801}, {"id": 67848, "content": "风油精缓解咽炎", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 59573}, {"id": 67849, "content": "早起毁一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 245, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 60125}, {"id": 67851, "content": "做完一小时瑜伽后简直一身轻松", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566617}, {"id": 68107, "content": "不开心的时候哭一场，心理会很舒服，心理压力也会减少", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540137}, {"id": 68365, "content": "心情不好不一定吃甜咸辣，也許在食很苦的時候，就那事算不了什麼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572295}, {"id": 67854, "content": "看球真的能让男人体会到与性爱不一样的高潮。", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260514}, {"id": 68110, "content": "说啥呢，第一次留言。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 571202}, {"id": 67855, "content": "一个人去海边", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 557943}, {"id": 67856, "content": "自拍", "image": "img/option/option/201606061616347s4AgcOXzFN3Bxya.jpg", "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 557943}, {"id": 68113, "content": "早睡早起真的身体好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 327264}, {"id": 68369, "content": "细嚼慢咽可以缓解便秘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572313}, {"id": 68115, "content": "喷嚏打不出来的时候看太阳。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 545432}, {"id": 67860, "content": "大牌包包真的让你更自信。", "image": null, "praise_count": 205, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 394195}, {"id": 67861, "content": "痛经吃止疼药的那位，对身体不好的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253533}, {"id": 68117, "content": "喉咙刚开始痛时，喝凉茶就能立刻不痛了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522436}, {"id": 69653, "content": "收拾了一整天的房间只需几个小时就会面目全非", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548420}, {"id": 67862, "content": "心情不好，去运动，尤其是游泳，把头埋在水下直到无法呼吸。在人只考虑完生存问题后，其他问题都不是事", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 554021}, {"id": 68118, "content": "不吃真的会瘦", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449816}, {"id": 67863, "content": "遇见的食物会很快再遇见一次！事物出现在生命中的概率增加，至少一加一。还有小时候做的梦第二天现实生活中全部再现。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569889}, {"id": 67864, "content": "如果睡不好真的毁一生", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 397771}, {"id": 67865, "content": "把家里收拾干净整齐整个人的状态都会清爽许多", "image": null, "praise_count": 180, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504299}, {"id": 68121, "content": "下雨夜更好睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202469}, {"id": 67866, "content": "最怕休假听到供应商的电话...", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566373}, {"id": 67867, "content": "听说喝可乐有助于防止老年痴呆 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569902}, {"id": 67868, "content": "遇到渣男再动心也要远离。", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 208642}, {"id": 67870, "content": "总会遇见不想遇见的人，总会发生不想发生的事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531192}, {"id": 68638, "content": "肚子痛的时候按虎口穴，亲测有效☺️", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 208086}, {"id": 67871, "content": "为小问题烦恼时 看看知乎上的提问，发现自己的问题都不是问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569927}, {"id": 67872, "content": "lol心态要好", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125594}, {"id": 68128, "content": "“读书”和“运动”，做了哪一件，这一天都会开心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 571264}, {"id": 67874, "content": "啪啪啪真的是世界上最爽的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 191, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107293}, {"id": 67875, "content": "我没意见 。耶！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568518}, {"id": 68131, "content": "健身房健身后快感很好的提升愉悅感受", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548967}, {"id": 67876, "content": "两块掐你买不了吃亏，两块钱你买不了上当。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530513}, {"id": 67877, "content": "便秘就喝星冰乐?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525605}, {"id": 68133, "content": "帮助别人，提升自已！内心存善念！整个世界充满爱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 571232}]}